{"tid":1845171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！原來高比係反侵左膠黎！","createTime":"2020-01-27T04:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T07:12:55.000Z","uid":20241,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b6c19db58328a4118ab4c777841460ec7241bfe9","tid":1845171,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"仲r唔rip好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hga5uq6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhga5uq6.png&h=baf7f556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f739e9c780a1f8db971657b02fbc367ece04cfb","tid":1845171,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">一日到黑就淨係錢, 樓價股價, 69已經話緊人收錢出黎行</span><br />\n會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#20241 - 高息股</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>我有一計可破黃色經濟圈 在此獻上希望可以俾個AO小妹做下 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>最近班黑衣暴徒越來越倡狂<br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n只要分出邊啲係黃店<br />\n再安排防暴長駐 入店既年青人全部都要查證+事後拘捕(擾亂社會秩序+非法集結)<br />\n咁樣黃色經濟圈好快就會不攻自破<br />\n香港好快可以回復正常<br />\n希望特首接納</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1802010/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1802010/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>冇事啦香港人贏左啦港女升返曬啦大家快啲返工返學啦 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>各位手足付出左咁多<br />\n贏得咁辛苦<br />\n大家俾啲掌聲自己好唔好<br />\n好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Flomoji%2F12.png&h=b2e0eb94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Flm2%2Fsupport.gif&h=4d4183e9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1758161/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1758161/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>水炮車其實都幾大部 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>支持警察係大街射死你地班暴徒<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1664677/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1664677/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>核彈都唔割！嗱不過搞裝修 紅綠燈 叫太多神獸就割架啦 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>始終人種同基因係咁就係咁<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fpig%2Fclap.gif&h=dc1b3984&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1628233/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1628233/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港太亂 希望政府強力執法 全港斷網 斷電話3日搜捕暴徒 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>周圍破壞 又上網亂咁抹黑警方同政府<br />\n我地一般市民真係忍唔到啦！<br />\n應立即斷網斷電話 實施戒嚴三日 趁呢段時間啲甲由冇得走一網打盡<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1618273/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1618273/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/4Re5r6q.png\" />"},{"pid":"a69934c16f3bbff1b73647e3a108da8b380c39e4","tid":1845171,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"死人都要拎出黎鞭？"},{"pid":"a5da7d49000251fd94240e33021fc5c066d33c89","tid":1845171,"uid":204539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:11:25.000Z","msg":"突你老母閪咩"},{"pid":"95635bfb9cf9a30370a589990195ef086219cd63","tid":1845171,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"定你想講所有rip佢嘅都係左膠？"},{"pid":"15338418fda22e4296beae9ee1df608ac0d10f37","tid":1845171,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"睇你信唔信因果。"},{"pid":"0c2ba348dad8c070f752315fa9ed7d755e1cf9d6","tid":1845171,"uid":66221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"果然樓主呢啲只會眨低手足嘅人都冇人性"},{"pid":"e0707f55c438683c15aacfd4096b6a12e54f5838","tid":1845171,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c2ba348dad8c070f752315fa9ed7d755e1cf9d6","tid":1845171,"uid":66221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"果然樓主呢啲只會眨低手足嘅人都冇人性"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"我幾時眨低手足？"},{"pid":"5a1089f57ea56cb07c1d4fbcf4962b536fa16b1d","tid":1845171,"uid":319628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"樓主想岀位？？"},{"pid"